Title: Adds the Saw Kill and the Fall Kill located in Dutchess county to the definition of inland waterways as a major creek
Summary: Relates to adding the Saw Kill and the Fall Kill located in Dutchess county to the definition of inland waterways as a major creek in order to make such waterway eligible for funding through the waterfront revitalization program.
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the executive law, in relation to adding the Saw Kill and Fall Kill creeks to the definition of inland waterways
